---
import SpotlightLayout from '../layouts/SpotlightLayout.astro';
import UiIcon from '../components/UiIcon.astro';
---

<SpotlightLayout title="关于我 | Joey's Notes" description="黄药师的个人介绍 - 软件工程师、摄影爱好者、猫奴">
  <section class="section-gap">
    <div class="shell">
      <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-5xl gap-12 lg:grid-cols-[1.2fr_0.8fr] lg:items-start">
        <div>
          <p class="eyebrow section-kicker"><UiIcon name="about" size={14} /> <span>About</span></p>
          <h1 class="mt-4 text-4xl font-semibold leading-tight sm:text-5xl" style="view-transition-name: site-identity-title;">我是黄药师，软件工程师与摄影爱好者</h1>

          <div class="mt-8 space-y-6 text-lg leading-8 muted">
            <p>拍拍照，养养猫，旅行和咖啡才是生活的主题，代码不过是对生活的消遣。</p>
            <p>我专注于 Web 开发和系统架构设计，喜欢把复杂问题拆解为可执行的工程步骤。</p>
            <p>这个博客记录技术实践与生活观察。如果内容对你有帮助，欢迎通过下方渠道联系我。</p>
          </div>

          <div class="about-links mt-10 grid gap-3 text-sm sm:grid-cols-2">
            <a href="https://github.com/oiahoon" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="soft-panel px-4 py-3 hover:border-[var(--accent)]"><UiIcon name="compass" size={14} /> <span>GitHub</span></a>
            <a href="https://weibo.com/desiver" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="soft-panel px-4 py-3 hover:border-[var(--accent)]"><UiIcon name="spark" size={14} /> <span>微博</span></a>
            <a href="/rss.xml" class="soft-panel px-4 py-3 hover:border-[var(--accent)]"><UiIcon name="rss" size={14} /> <span>RSS 订阅</span></a>
            <a href="mailto:4296411@qq.com" class="soft-panel px-4 py-3 hover:border-[var(--accent)]"><UiIcon name="article" size={14} /> <span>4296411@qq.com</span></a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mx-auto w-full max-w-sm lg:mx-0">
          <img src="/img/avatar-joey.jpg" alt="Joey Huang" class="w-full rounded-2xl object-cover" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</SpotlightLayout>

<style>
  .about-links a {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.48rem;
  }

  .about-links :global(.ui-icon) {
    color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--accent) 64%, var(--muted));
    opacity: 0.72;
  }
</style>
